<Layout
	title="AGA Appliance Repair | Factory-Trained Experts Near You"
	description="Your AGA appliance is more than a cooking tool—it's a symbol of tradition, craftsmanship, and timeless elegance. Whether it’s a classic cast-iron range, a Total Control series oven, or a Companion cooker, this British icon deserves nothing less than white-glove care."
	structuredData={structuredData}
>
<ParallaxHeader client:idle/>
<div class="wrapper" id="webpage">
<section id="webpage">
  <h1>AGA Appliance Repair | Factory-Trained Experts Near You</h1>
  <div>
 <img width="500" height="500" loading="lazy" class="image-left" src="/aga/aga-appliance-repair-technician.webp" alt="AGA appliance repair services" width="500">
  <p>Your AGA appliance is more than a cooking tool—it's a symbol of tradition, craftsmanship, and timeless elegance. Whether it’s a classic cast-iron range, a Total Control series oven, or a Companion cooker, this British icon deserves nothing less than white-glove care.</p>
  <p>At <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci</strong>, we specialize in AGA appliance repair, offering expert service that protects the beauty, functionality, and legacy of your premium appliance. If your AGA isn’t heating properly, experiencing electrical issues, or simply needs a performance tune-up—we’re the trusted team to call.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>Why Choose Zaricci for AGA Appliance Repair?</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Certified Technicians with AGA Expertise:</strong> AGA appliances are uniquely built. Our technicians are specially trained to handle their radiant heat systems, gas and electric conversions, and precision thermostats—ensuring every repair is performed with exacting attention to detail.</li>
    <li><strong>Genuine AGA Parts Only:</strong> We use manufacturer-approved components for all AGA repairs, preserving your appliance’s performance, safety, and warranty.</li>
    <li><strong>Quick & Flexible Appointments:</strong> We offer same-day or next-day service in many areas because we understand that a broken AGA disrupts your entire kitchen flow.</li>
    <li><strong>Transparent Pricing, No Guesswork:</strong> You'll receive a clear, upfront estimate before any work begins—no hidden fees, no surprises.</li>
  </ul>
</section>
<section>
  <h3 id="service">Common AGA Appliance Issues We Repair</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Oven Not Heating or Overheating:</strong> We diagnose and repair AGA’s radiant heat elements, thermostats, and flue systems to restore even, consistent cooking performance.</li>
    <li><strong>Pilot Light or Burner Issues:</strong> If your AGA runs on gas and won’t light, or the flame is inconsistent, we repair or replace the burners, valves, or thermocouples as needed.</li>
    <li><strong>Electrical Control Problems:</strong> For modern AGA models, we handle digital control panel failures, temperature fluctuations, and programming errors.</li>
    <li><strong>Enamel Damage or Aesthetic Restoration:</strong> We take care to preserve or restore AGA’s signature vitreous enamel finishes, giving your appliance a like-new appearance.</li>
    <li><strong>AGA Total Control Series Issues:</strong> From touchscreen problems to heat-up time delays, our technicians are trained to resolve smart system malfunctions with precision.</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>We Service All AGA Models, Including:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>AGA Classic Cast Iron Ranges</li>
    <li>AGA Total Control Series</li>
    <li>AGA Dual Control & City60</li>
    <li>AGA eR3 and eR7 Electric Series</li>
    <li>AGA Companion & Module Units</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>The Zaricci Repair Process – Luxury Service from Start to Finish</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Contact Us Online or By Phone:</strong> Let us know the issue, model, and your availability—we'll schedule a visit that works for you.</li>
    <li><strong>Precision Diagnosis:</strong> A brand-certified Zaricci technician will arrive promptly and inspect your AGA appliance with care and expertise.</li>
    <li><strong>Upfront Repair Plan:</strong> You’ll receive a transparent quote covering all parts, labor, and expected timelines before we begin.</li>
    <li><strong>Expert Repairs with Authentic Parts:</strong> We complete your repair using only genuine AGA parts, ensuring long-term performance and peace of mind.</li>
    <li><strong>Final Testing & Satisfaction Guarantee:</strong> We rigorously test every component and back our work with a service warranty, so you can cook with confidence.</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>Proudly Serving Luxury Homes Across Southern California</h3>
  <p>Whether you live in Los Angeles, Beverly Hills, Santa Monica, or anywhere in the surrounding area, <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci</strong> delivers top-tier service that meets the demands of homeowners who expect nothing but the best.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>AGA Is Special. So Are We.</h3>
  <p>Your AGA isn’t just another appliance—it’s the centerpiece of your kitchen, a gathering place, and a conversation starter. At <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci</strong>, we treat it with the respect, knowledge, and craftsmanship it deserves.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>📞 Ready to Restore Your AGA?</h3>
  <p>Don't let heating problems, control issues, or cosmetic wear stand between you and your perfect kitchen experience.</p>
  <p><strong>✅ Call now</strong> or schedule your AGA appliance repair online for service that’s as refined as your appliance.</p>
  <p><strong>👉 Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci</strong> – Where Timeless Appliances Meet Expert Care.</p>
</section>

